long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Browser extension to investigate Datadog Browser SDK integration by:
- displaying collected events
- visualising the render of recorded events
- visualising the SDK configuration and active session
- configuring the SDK used and its behaviour
